#  11. AMD Zen (MZEN) (NEW)
#  12. AMD Zen 2 (MZEN2) (NEW)
#  13. AMD Zen 3 (MZEN3) (NEW)
#  14. AMD Zen 4 (MZEN4) (NEW)
#  15. Intel P4 / older Netburst based Xeon (MPSC)
#  16. Intel Core 2 (MCORE2)
#  17. Intel Atom (MATOM)
#  18. Intel Nehalem (MNEHALEM) (NEW)
