#  20. Intel Silvermont (MSILVERMONT) (NEW)
#  21. Intel Goldmont (MGOLDMONT) (NEW)
#  22. Intel Goldmont Plus (MGOLDMONTPLUS) (NEW)
#  23. Intel Sandy Bridge (MSANDYBRIDGE) (NEW)
#  24. Intel Ivy Bridge (MIVYBRIDGE) (NEW)
